sql: SELECT icu_admit.icu_type, AVG(admit.los) AS average_los FROM (SELECT icu.SUBJECT_ID, icu.HADM_ID, CASE WHEN trf1.FIRST_CAREUNIT LIKE '%Emergency%' AND trf2.FIRST_CAREUNIT LIKE '%ICU%' THEN 'Direct_ER_to_ICU' WHEN trf1.FIRST_CAREUNIT NOT LIKE '%ICU%' AND trf2.FIRST_CAREUNIT LIKE '%ICU%' THEN 'Ward_to_ICU' ELSE 'Other' END AS icu_type FROM TRANSFERS trf1 INNER JOIN TRANSFERS trf2 ON trf1.SUBJECT_ID = trf2.SUBJECT_ID AND trf1.HADM_ID = trf2.HADM_ID INNER JOIN ICUSTAYS icu ON trf2.SUBJECT_ID = icu.SUBJECT_ID AND trf2.HADM_ID = icu.HADM_ID AND trf2.INTIME = icu.INTIME WHERE icu.FIRST_CAREUNIT IS NOT NULL AND (trf1.FIRST_CAREUNIT LIKE '%Ward%' OR trf1.FIRST_CAREUNIT LIKE '%Emergency%') AND trf2.FIRST_CAREUNIT LIKE '%ICU%') icu_admit JOIN (SELECT SUBJECT_ID, HADM_ID, (CAST(DISCHTIME AS DATE) - CAST(ADMITTIME AS DATE)) AS los FROM ADMISSIONS WHERE ADMITTIME IS NOT NULL AND DISCHTIME IS NOT NULL) admit ON icu_admit.SUBJECT_ID = admit.SUBJECT_ID AND icu_admit.HADM_ID = admit.HADM_ID GROUP BY icu_admit.icu_type

sql: WITH first_icu AS ( SELECT i.SUBJECT_ID, i.HADM_ID, MIN(i.INTIME) AS FIRST_ICU_INTIME FROM ICUSTAYS i WHERE i.INTIME IS NOT NULL GROUP BY i.SUBJECT_ID, i.HADM_ID ), pre_icu AS ( SELECT f.SUBJECT_ID, f.HADM_ID, MAX(CASE WHEN t.CAREUNIT IS NOT NULL AND UPPER(t.CAREUNIT) NOT LIKE '%ICU%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS HAS_NON_ICU_BEFORE FROM first_icu f LEFT JOIN TRANSFERS t ON t.SUBJECT_ID = f.SUBJECT_ID AND t.HADM_ID = f.HADM_ID AND NVL(t.OUTTIME, t.INTIME) < f.FIRST_ICU_INTIME GROUP BY f.SUBJECT_ID, f.HADM_ID ), path_labeled AS ( SELECT f.SUBJECT_ID, f.HADM_ID, CASE WHEN UPPER(NVL(a.ADMISSION_LOCATION, '')) LIKE '%EMERGENCY%' AND NVL(p.HAS_NON_ICU_BEFORE, 0) = 0 THEN 'Direct_ER_to_ICU' WHEN NVL(p.HAS_NON_ICU_BEFORE, 0) = 1 THEN 'Ward_to_ICU' ELSE 'Other' END AS ICU_PATH FROM first_icu f JOIN ADMISSIONS a ON a.SUBJECT_ID = f.SUBJECT_ID AND a.HADM_ID = f.HADM_ID LEFT JOIN pre_icu p ON p.SUBJECT_ID = f.SUBJECT_ID AND p.HADM_ID = f.HADM_ID ) SELECT l.ICU_PATH, COUNT(*) AS ADMISSION_CNT, AVG(CAST(a.DISCHTIME AS DATE) - CAST(a.ADMITTIME AS DATE)) AS AVG_HOSPITAL_LOS FROM path_labeled l JOIN ADMISSIONS a ON a.SUBJECT_ID = l.SUBJECT_ID AND a.HADM_ID = l.HADM_ID WHERE l.ICU_PATH IN ('Direct_ER_to_ICU', 'Ward_to_ICU') AND a.ADMITTIME IS NOT NULL AND a.DISCHTIME IS NOT NULL GROUP BY l.ICU_PATH ORDER BY l.ICU_PATH

question: 성별/연령별 진단 분포

sql:
SELECT diag_age_group, icd.LONG_TITLE, COUNT(*) AS CNT
FROM (
    SELECT CASE 
               WHEN p.ANCHOR_AGE BETWEEN 0 AND 19 THEN '0-19'
               WHEN p.ANCHOR_AGE BETWEEN 20 AND 39 THEN '20-39'
               WHEN p.ANCHOR_AGE BETWEEN 40 AND 59 THEN '40-59'
               WHEN p.ANCHOR_AGE BETWEEN 60 AND 79 THEN '60-79'
               ELSE '80+' 
           END AS diag_age_group,
           d_icd.ICD_CODE, d_icd.ICD_VERSION
    FROM DIAGNOSES_ICD d_icd
    INNER JOIN PATIENTS p ON d_icd.SUBJECT_ID = p.SUBJECT_ID
    WHERE p.GENDER = 'M'
) age_diag
INNER JOIN D_ICD_DIAGNOSES icd ON age_diag.ICD_CODE = icd.ICD_CODE AND age_diag.ICD_VERSION = icd.ICD_VERSION
WHERE LOWER(icd.LONG_TITLE) LIKE '%heart disease%'
GROUP BY diag_age_group, icd.LONG_TITLE

question: loop diuretics(예: furosemide) 사용량 사분위수(Q1–Q4)에 따른 AKI 진단 비율을 비교해줘.
sql:
WITH loop_rx AS ( 
    SELECT p.HADM_ID, SUM(NVL(p.doses_per_24_hrs, 0)) AS loop_dose 
    FROM PRESCRIPTIONS p 
    WHERE ROWNUM <= 5000 AND p.HADM_ID IS NOT NULL 
    AND (LOWER(p.drug) LIKE '%furosemide%' OR LOWER(p.drug) LIKE '%bumetanide%' OR LOWER(p.drug) LIKE '%torsemide%' OR LOWER(p.drug) LIKE '%ethacrynic%' OR LOWER(p.drug) LIKE '%loop diuretic%') 
    GROUP BY p.HADM_ID 
), 
dose_q AS ( 
    SELECT HADM_ID, loop_dose, NTILE(4) OVER (ORDER BY loop_dose) AS qtile 
    FROM loop_rx 
), 
aki_hadm AS ( 
    SELECT DISTINCT d.HADM_ID 
    FROM DIAGNOSES_ICD d 
    WHERE (d.icd_version = 10 AND d.icd_code LIKE 'N17%') 
    OR (d.icd_version = 9 AND d.icd_code LIKE '584%') 
) 
SELECT 'Q' || q.qtile AS dose_quartile, 
       COUNT(DISTINCT q.HADM_ID) AS n_hadm, 
       COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN a.HADM_ID IS NOT NULL THEN q.HADM_ID END) AS n_aki_hadm, 
       ROUND(100 * COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN a.HADM_ID IS NOT NULL THEN q.HADM_ID END) / NULLIF(COUNT(DISTINCT q.HADM_ID), 0), 2) AS aki_diagnosis_rate_pct 
FROM dose_q q 
LEFT JOIN aki_hadm a ON a.HADM_ID = q.HADM_ID 
GROUP BY q.qtile 
ORDER BY q.qtile

question: 푸로세미드 사용량 사분위수(Q1-Q4)별 병원 사망률을 비교해줘.
sql:
WITH furosemide_usage AS ( 
    SELECT p.HADM_ID, SUM(NVL(p.doses_per_24_hrs, 0)) AS total_dose 
    FROM PRESCRIPTIONS p 
    WHERE LOWER(p.drug) LIKE '%furosemide%' 
    GROUP BY p.HADM_ID 
), 
usage_quartiles AS ( 
    SELECT HADM_ID, total_dose, NTILE(4) OVER (ORDER BY total_dose) AS quartile 
    FROM furosemide_usage 
), 
mortality AS ( 
    SELECT HADM_ID 
    FROM ADMISSIONS 
    WHERE HOSPITAL_EXPIRE_FLAG = 1 
) 
SELECT 'Q' || u.quartile AS dose_quartile, 
       COUNT(DISTINCT u.HADM_ID) AS n_hadm, 
       COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN m.HADM_ID IS NOT NULL THEN u.HADM_ID END) AS n_mortality, 
       ROUND(100 * COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN m.HADM_ID IS NOT NULL THEN u.HADM_ID END) / NULLIF(COUNT(DISTINCT u.HADM_ID), 0), 2) AS mortality_rate_pct 
FROM usage_quartiles u 
LEFT JOIN mortality m ON m.HADM_ID = u.HADM_ID 
GROUP BY u.quartile 
ORDER BY u.quartile

ORDER BY u.quartile

question: Compare AKI diagnosis rate by quartile (Q1-Q4) of loop diuretics usage, such as furosemide.
sql:
WITH loop_rx AS ( 
    SELECT p.HADM_ID, SUM(NVL(p.doses_per_24_hrs, 0)) AS loop_dose 
    FROM PRESCRIPTIONS p 
    WHERE p.HADM_ID IS NOT NULL 
    AND (LOWER(p.drug) LIKE '%furosemide%' 
         OR LOWER(p.drug) LIKE '%bumetanide%' 
         OR LOWER(p.drug) LIKE '%torsemide%' 
         OR LOWER(p.drug) LIKE '%ethacrynic%' 
         OR LOWER(p.drug) LIKE '%loop diuretic%') 
    GROUP BY p.HADM_ID 
), 
dose_q AS ( 
    SELECT HADM_ID, loop_dose, NTILE(4) OVER (ORDER BY loop_dose) AS qtile 
    FROM loop_rx 
), 
aki_hadm AS ( 
    SELECT DISTINCT d.HADM_ID 
    FROM DIAGNOSES_ICD d 
    WHERE (d.icd_version = 10 AND d.icd_code LIKE 'N17%') 
       OR (d.icd_version = 9 AND d.icd_code LIKE '584%') 
) 
SELECT 'Q' || q.qtile AS dose_quartile, 
       COUNT(DISTINCT q.HADM_ID) AS n_hadm, 
       COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN a.HADM_ID IS NOT NULL THEN q.HADM_ID END) AS n_aki_hadm, 
       ROUND(100 * COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN a.HADM_ID IS NOT NULL THEN q.HADM_ID END) / NULLIF(COUNT(DISTINCT q.HADM_ID), 0), 2) AS aki_diagnosis_rate_pct 
FROM dose_q q 
LEFT JOIN aki_hadm a ON a.HADM_ID = q.HADM_ID 
GROUP BY q.qtile 
ORDER BY q.qtile
